{"tid":1139332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大公報︰內地遊客疑在香港打到水貨疫苗","createTime":"2019-05-05T07:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T01:43:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":276,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"cb83fadace749db2992366d3b619878856ff4895","tid":1139332,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.takungpao.com/2019/0503/20190503031801699.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.takungpao.com%2F2019%2F0503%2F20190503031801699.jpg&h=d870dd2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日是內地「五一」假期第二天，大批內地女遊客趁機來港接種九價子宮頸癌（HPV）疫苗，迫爆各區接種診所，私家診所生意大增，有旅客表明來港只為注射疫苗，花錢打針比購物還要多。《大公報》獨家揭露「水貨九價HPV疫苗」，事件持續發酵，不少曾在不同診所打針的內地客，細讀《大公報》後紛表擔心，恐健康受損，有的更徬徨說：「我的經歷與報道所寫一樣，該怎麼辦？」有曾接種「水貨疫苗」的內地苦主更計劃來港追究，「好想衛生署幫嚇我哋，伸張正義，討番個公道！」<br />\n<br />\n  尖沙咀及佐敦一帶傳統遊客區，在「五一」期間迫滿內地客，但部分人的目的不是到商場購物，而是到樓上診所接種疫苗。據記者觀察，不少專門施打疫苗的診所，迫滿「帶埋行李篋」接種疫苗的旅客，一家僅百多二百呎的診所內，高峰期塞滿超過五十人。他們大部分都是透過微信或網上找中介公司預約打針，三針九價HPV疫苗，費用由六、七千至近萬元人民幣不等。內地旅客張女士透露，一家四口來港打各種疫苗，預計花超過一萬五千元人民幣。「香港疫苗質素有保證，總不可能有水貨吧？」<br />\n<br />\n  「我看《大公報》後，才知道自己不幸中招了！」現年24歲的陳小姐（化名）透露，去年8月24日付了9000港元給中介，預約到於旺角某辦公大樓L醫生的診所，從南京來港注射九價HPV疫苗。她憶述，甫接觸中屆時已覺不妥，心想為什麼明明有報道指香港九價HPV疫苗短缺，但中介卻可大拍心口稱只要早兩、三天預約，就可以安排接種？「那時候自己心急接種，也沒再多想了。」<br />\n<br />\n  L醫生手寫聲明 沒提從何地進口<br />\n<br />\n  陳小姐憶述，在第一次接種時，曾向L醫生要求檢查疫苗包裝，詎料L醫生只從抽屜取出一個空的針盒讓她查看，旋即收回，並開始施打疫苗。「我連上面的註冊號碼及名字都還沒來得及看清，他就收走針盒，讓我開始有點警覺及懷疑。注射完之後，我向他要求取走針盒，以便日後有任何不適也可以有所證明，但醫生的說法就是不可以帶走。」<br />\n<br />\n  相隔兩個月，陳小姐再按時到該診所接種第二針。「因為醫生拆包裝時十分閃縮，所以我特地留意他手上的針劑，結果發現疫苗包裝膠套上並沒有MSD公司註冊標誌。」這次接種後，陳小姐長期出現嚴重頭痛徵狀，影響精神及工作。回南京後，她更先後三次花費逾萬元人民幣，到當地最頂尖的醫院進行磁力共振等檢查，卻查不出病因，醫生只能推斷是注射疫苗引起的後遺症。<br />\n<br />\n  其後，陳小姐透過中介打算向診所追究，診所卻傳來一張有L醫生簽署的手寫聲明，上面寫着「醫務所提供的HPV 9價疫苗全部均為美國默沙東藥廠生產的針劑」，惟聲明中L醫生沒有提及疫苗從何地進口。診所在安撫陳小姐同時亦施「嚇招」：「之前客（人）一家幾口打完第一針，然後話我哋打假貨，要求賠錢，後來他們報埋警。警方話不受理他們，現在我們反告番他們損害診所及醫生名譽，正交律師處理。」<br />\n<br />\n  陳小姐對診所的回應氣憤不已：「沒想到注射沒註冊疫苗的診所還會這麼囂張，對香港的醫療監管體系已經失去信心，我認為衛生署等政府部門監督巡查不力，絕對會追究到底！」<br />\n<br />\n  另一名苦主郭小姐（化名）更表示，注射第一針九價HPV疫苗時正值感冒，身體不適，當其向診所護士查詢對接種有否影響時，該護士不以為然稱「通通沒影響」。進入診症室後，更是由一名沒有表明身份的女士為其接種疫苗，直至數天前打第三針才由L醫生主理。「當時已經看到大家說這家診所有點問題，結果打完之後，我就一直頭暈不適。」郭小姐怒斥診所無良，計劃組織其他苦主來港，向衛生署及醫務委員會作出投訴，力求討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/life/238150/2019/0503/283289.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Flife%2F238150%2F2019%2F0503%2F283289.html&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2yx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=9174a55a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/life/238150/2019/0503/283289.html</a>"},{"pid":"26825745d1086c08d3b36eb5a22ec8a2c8778241","tid":1139332,"uid":89134,"like":244,"dislike":0,"score":244,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"唔好嚟香港"},{"pid":"0398eac173db8e50e45838a067acc25a5a5dd968","tid":1139332,"uid":56453,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec0840bb25a355825d312dc5bc3f10a6341caea","tid":1139332,"uid":54264,"like":216,"dislike":0,"score":216,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"水貨疫苗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁鐘意走水貨岩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369d116569e1d1756718035191edfc12df821531","tid":1139332,"uid":152476,"like":211,"dislike":0,"score":211,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"真係好仆街<br />\n要廣傳等中國人唔好再去香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6469a9d428976fc814ceac9edda9328b4bda57c","tid":1139332,"uid":37596,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"支那人打支那疫苗係合情合理合法"},{"pid":"9a412369d333a46a035381a5ac646883d7f39870","tid":1139332,"uid":100347,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"有乜咁奇<br />\n<br />\n良心診所"},{"pid":"a30ac0a144555459704cb512f05564ad3c1d51a3","tid":1139332,"uid":79410,"like":196,"dislike":0,"score":196,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"大公報做乜報D 唔報D 呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做支那版同香港版唔同? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據觀察，這家診所行事神秘，辦公大樓門口沒有任何門牌指示，反而用另家一醫美中心作為掩護。而L醫生平日處事亦十分小心，只會為內地人接種疫苗，不接受香港市民上門，客人要注射疫苗，只能通過診所合作的中介預約。客人進入診症室前，職員首先必須查驗內地遊客身份，有內地身份證者才允許進入。而在收取診金時，診所只接受現金，或中介先收費，謝絕客人以信用卡等可追查消費紀錄的方式付款，儘管如此，該診所依舊生意興隆，一天的銷售額估計可高達二十萬元。<br />\n<br />\n而在記者曝光後，該診所的保安變得更加嚴密，只許接種疫苗的客人單獨進入，陪同人士均被拒門外。診所門口貼有告示，寫著&ldquo;由於近日流行麻疹等空氣及飛沫傳染病，為減低疾病傳播風險，所有到本診所接受疫苗人士，除接受注射之本人外，其他人或家屬請勿進入及逗留本診所。&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://new.qq.com/omn/20190503/20190503A02UVJ.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Fomn%2F20190503%2F20190503A02UVJ.html&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2yx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=5ba13cc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://new.qq.com/omn/20190503/20190503A02UVJ.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔關香港人事, 支那人你死你事, 香港人唔會打到呢D 水貨疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a438a5d6688619aa1f4b6b8dea8ba07eebd56f7","tid":1139332,"uid":28831,"like":112,"dislike":0,"score":112,"quote":{"pid":"a30ac0a144555459704cb512f05564ad3c1d51a3","tid":1139332,"uid":79410,"like":196,"dislike":0,"score":196,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"大公報做乜報D 唔報D 呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做支那版同香港版唔同? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據觀察，這家診所行事神秘，辦公大樓門口沒有任何門牌指示，反而用另家一醫美中心作為掩護。而L醫生平日處事亦十分小心，只會為內地人接種疫苗，不接受香港市民上門，客人要注射疫苗，只能通過診所合作的中介預約。客人進入診症室前，職員首先必須查驗內地遊客身份，有內地身份證者才允許進入。而在收取診金時，診所只接受現金，或中介先收費，謝絕客人以信用卡等可追查消費紀錄的方式付款，儘管如此，該診所依舊生意興隆，一天的銷售額估計可高達二十萬元。<br />\n<br />\n而在記者曝光後，該診所的保安變得更加嚴密，只許接種疫苗的客人單獨進入，陪同人士均被拒門外。診所門口貼有告示，寫著&ldquo;由於近日流行麻疹等空氣及飛沫傳染病，為減低疾病傳播風險，所有到本診所接受疫苗人士，除接受注射之本人外，其他人或家屬請勿進入及逗留本診所。&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://new.qq.com/omn/20190503/20190503A02UVJ.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Fomn%2F20190503%2F20190503A02UVJ.html&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2yx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=5ba13cc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://new.qq.com/omn/20190503/20190503A02UVJ.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔關香港人事, 支那人你死你事, 香港人唔會打到呢D 水貨疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心都涼曬<br />\n蝗金週最開心嘅新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e722dc36379a2e63f79da2e931ef0a6bd108067","tid":1139332,"uid":23635,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:51:18.000Z","msg":"強国人專登落香港打強国疫苗，成件事好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d8a65f0ca289d07b4667e37b3696d1c03b91fe","tid":1139332,"uid":152476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3a438a5d6688619aa1f4b6b8dea8ba07eebd56f7","tid":1139332,"uid":28831,"like":112,"dislike":0,"score":112,"quote":{"pid":"a30ac0a144555459704cb512f05564ad3c1d51a3","tid":1139332,"uid":79410,"like":196,"dislike":0,"score":196,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"大公報做乜報D 唔報D 呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做支那版同香港版唔同? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據觀察，這家診所行事神秘，辦公大樓門口沒有任何門牌指示，反而用另家一醫美中心作為掩護。而L醫生平日處事亦十分小心，只會為內地人接種疫苗，不接受香港市民上門，客人要注射疫苗，只能通過診所合作的中介預約。客人進入診症室前，職員首先必須查驗內地遊客身份，有內地身份證者才允許進入。而在收取診金時，診所只接受現金，或中介先收費，謝絕客人以信用卡等可追查消費紀錄的方式付款，儘管如此，該診所依舊生意興隆，一天的銷售額估計可高達二十萬元。<br />\n<br />\n而在記者曝光後，該診所的保安變得更加嚴密，只許接種疫苗的客人單獨進入，陪同人士均被拒門外。診所門口貼有告示，寫著&ldquo;由於近日流行麻疹等空氣及飛沫傳染病，為減低疾病傳播風險，所有到本診所接受疫苗人士，除接受注射之本人外，其他人或家屬請勿進入及逗留本診所。&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://new.qq.com/omn/20190503/20190503A02UVJ.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Fomn%2F20190503%2F20190503A02UVJ.html&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2yx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=5ba13cc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://new.qq.com/omn/20190503/20190503A02UVJ.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔關香港人事, 支那人你死你事, 香港人唔會打到呢D 水貨疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心都涼曬<br />\n蝗金週最開心嘅新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:52:30.000Z","msg":"哇？咁都得！<br />\n唔好再去香港啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bac3a508b2a419cad13f6b34447d30b313d0c67","tid":1139332,"uid":155818,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"6e722dc36379a2e63f79da2e931ef0a6bd108067","tid":1139332,"uid":23635,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:51:18.000Z","msg":"強国人專登落香港打強国疫苗，成件事好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:52:38.000Z","msg":"香港人唔比打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e065a85bea5e9fa6260551bfac4226b6617583","tid":1139332,"uid":28195,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"香港水貨都係美國貨，你大公報吹咩<br />\n<br />\n中共大陸貨係假貨，會死人架"},{"pid":"926a314cc713557f3e7d7b1d331cdc7d82dae9e6","tid":1139332,"uid":79410,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢真係好有醫德. <br />\n同部份D 藥房一樣. 賣返D 支那假貨俾支那人. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b20ba0713cf9838e38d74b1f5c099793eabb2fe","tid":1139332,"uid":37502,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"「好想衛生署幫